comments: LeVert (BKN) briefly places a hand on James' (LAL) back, as he is sliding it off it then makes contact with the ball during the driving shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) places his arm across LeVert's (BKN) body while attempting to defend the screen. The contact is exaggerated after the two make contact with Prince (BKN) who is setting the screen.
Prince (BKN) makes slight contact to James' (LAL) arm at the end of the drive during the pass.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Green (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during Dinwiddie's (BKN) driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) makes marginal contact with Jordan's (BKN) arm while attempting to secure the rebound.
Jordan (BKN) gathers the loose ball on his right foot. Jordan then lifts his pivot foot and returns it to the floor without releasing the ball.
Green (LAL) initiates contact with Jordan (BKN) that affects his FOM after he gathers the loose ball.
Bradley's (LAL) left arm collapses to his body while he reaches in with his other hand that does not make contact to Dinwiddie's (BKN) arm during the drive.
LeVert (BKN) makes marginal contact to James' (LAL) back as he spins and changes direction during his driving shot attempt.
Dinwwide (BKN) makes contact with the ball and cleanly deflects it away from Davis (LAL) as he attempts to gather the loose ball.
Green (LAL) and Dinwiddie (BKN) mutually engage in marginal contact during the the loose ball.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Chandler's (BKN) path as he is firming up when the contact occurs.
After communication with the Replay Center, the call on the floor is confirmed and the Lakers retains possession of the ball.
